    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are on a service to detect and destroy mimics - alien creatures capable of taking the form of any object.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280980/extras/dd368b78e5cc140cce9fc415b0cd4dcd.poster.avif?t=1754456001\" width=600 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280980/extras/dd368b78e5cc140cce9fc415b0cd4dcd.webm?t=1754456001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280980/extras/dd368b78e5cc140cce9fc415b0cd4dcd.mp4?t=1754456001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You patrol the location, scrutinizing it for mimics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They can give themselves away in a number of ways. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some just look strange and don't fit in the environment, others make sounds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many different kinds of mimics and they're getting smarter and better....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you miss a mimic you lose and have to start over. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paranoia-inducing gameplay.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different unlockable locations.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different types of mimics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless Mode.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
